{"type":null,"faqId":13070,"title":"H30-L01&H30-L02  手机发热量大，如何解决？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>手机发热主要取决于您使用手机的方式。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>充电时手机发热：充电时发热是普遍现象。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>针对这点华为手机在设计时增加了过热保护电路功能，确保不会因为发热导致电池发生故障或寿命缩短。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>请尽量在阴凉干燥的地方充电。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>另外，建议您不要在充电时进行上网、玩游戏或看视频等高功耗的操作。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">玩游戏时手机发热：玩游戏时，手机</span><span> CPU </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">处于高负载状态，会产生较大热量</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>但华为手机均通过国家安规测试，正常使用时的发热不会产生安全风险。建议玩游戏时彻底关闭后台暂时不使用的应用程序，同时请不要在充电时玩游戏。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>使用数据网络时手机发热：使用数据网络时手机的发热程度主要与网络信号强度有关，信号较差时手机发热较大。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>建议您移动到信号强度大的地方后再连接网络。另外，尽量不要开启大量第三方应用程序同时获取网络资源，这样不仅会造成流量突增，同时会增加手机的发热量。在网络信号较弱的地方，尽量不要长时间充电时上网。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:Wingdings;font-size:8pt;\"><span>l</span></span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>通话时手机发热：请尽量在信号强度较大的地方通话，同时建议您使用耳机进行通话。</span></span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\"><span>华为会定期在官网发布最新软件版本，以优化软件性能，请您及时升级软件，以体验更好的手机性能。</span></span> \n</p>","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":3,"unUseful":6,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"4023","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1401961499000,"seriesProductName":"H30-L01,H30-L02","visitedTimes":674,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":5,"times":1,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":5.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}